RIBELIN
v.
CREEL. No. 112A15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. Robert L. Inge, Attorney at Law, Salisbury, For Creel, Phillip Ray. Phillip Creel, For Creel, Phillip Ray. Arlaine Rockey, Attorney at Law, Marshall, For Ribelin, Dana Marie (fka Creel).

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of March 2015 by Plaintiff-Appellant to Accept Corrected Certificate of Filing and Service:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
